Package: acor
Type: Package
Title: Asymmetric Correlation Measures
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Eva-Maria", family = "Walz", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "evamaria.walz@gmx.de")
    )
Description: Computes and tests correlation measures: AKC (Asymmetric Kendall Correlation),
    AGC (Asymmetric Grade Correlation), CID (Concordance-Discordance Index), and CMA
    (Coefficient of Monotone Association). Supports single and multiple predictors, IID and
    time-series (HAC) variance estimation. Methods are described in
    Walz (2025) <arXiv:>.
